00050 void CHPFileWriterTest::WriteExpressionTest()
00051 {
00052         CHPData data("CHP_expression_file", CHP_EXPRESSION_ASSAY_TYPE);
00053         data.SetEntryCount(2, 16, true);
00054         data.SetBackgroundZoneCnt(2);
00055         writer = new CHPFileWriter(data);
00056 
00057         CHPExpressionEntry e1("probe set 1",10,11.0f,17.8f,6,5,true,2,56.9f,45.89f,42.0f,47.0f,2);
00058         CHPExpressionEntry e2("probe set 2",10,1.0f,7.8f,6,5,true,2,5.9f,4.89f,2.0f,7.0f,2);
00059         writer->SeekToDataSet();
00060         writer->WriteExpressionEntry(e1);
00061         writer->WriteExpressionEntry(e2);
00062 
00063         CHPBackgroundZone bgz1(11.0f,17.8f,56.9f,45.89f);
00064         CHPBackgroundZone bgz2(1.0f,7.8f,6.9f,5.89f);
00065         writer->SeekToBgSet();
00066         writer->WriteBackgroundZone(bgz1);
00067         writer->WriteBackgroundZone(bgz2);
00068         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(1);
00069 
00070         delete writer;
00071 
00072 
00073         CHPFileReader reader;
00074         reader.SetFilename("CHP_expression_file");
00075         CHPData data2;
00076         reader.Read(data2);
00077 
00078         CHPExpressionEntry e;
00079         data2.GetEntry(0, e);
00080         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(e.GetProbeSetName() == e1.GetProbeSetName());
00081         CPPUNIT_ASSERT_DOUBLES_EQUAL(e.GetSignal(), e1.GetSignal(), 0.000001f);
00082         CPPUNIT_ASSERT_DOUBLES_EQUAL(e.GetDetectionPValue(), e1.GetDetectionPValue(), 0.000001f);
00083         CPPUNIT_ASSERT_DOUBLES_EQUAL(e.GetChangePValue(), e1.GetChangePValue(), 0.000001f);
00084         CPPUNIT_ASSERT_DOUBLES_EQUAL(e.GetSigLogRatio(), e1.GetSigLogRatio(), 0.000001f);
00085         CPPUNIT_ASSERT_DOUBLES_EQUAL(e.GetSigLogRatioLo(), e1.GetSigLogRatioLo(), 0.000001f);
00086         CPPUNIT_ASSERT_DOUBLES_EQUAL(e.GetSigLogRatioHi(), e1.GetSigLogRatioHi(), 0.000001f);
00087         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(e.GetDetection() ==e1.GetDetection());
00088         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(e.GetNumPairs() ==e1.GetNumPairs());
00089         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(e.GetNumPairsUsed() ==e1.GetNumPairsUsed());
00090         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(e.GetHasComparisonData() ==e1.GetHasComparisonData());
00091         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(e.GetChange() ==e1.GetChange());
00092         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(e.GetCommonPairs() ==e1.GetCommonPairs());
00093 
00094         data2.GetEntry(1, e);
00095         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(e.GetProbeSetName() == e2.GetProbeSetName());
00096         CPPUNIT_ASSERT_DOUBLES_EQUAL(e.GetSignal(), e2.GetSignal(), 0.000001f);
00097         CPPUNIT_ASSERT_DOUBLES_EQUAL(e.GetDetectionPValue(), e2.GetDetectionPValue(), 0.000001f);
00098         CPPUNIT_ASSERT_DOUBLES_EQUAL(e.GetChangePValue(), e2.GetChangePValue(), 0.000001f);
00099         CPPUNIT_ASSERT_DOUBLES_EQUAL(e.GetSigLogRatio(), e2.GetSigLogRatio(), 0.000001f);
00100         CPPUNIT_ASSERT_DOUBLES_EQUAL(e.GetSigLogRatioLo(), e2.GetSigLogRatioLo(), 0.000001f);
00101         CPPUNIT_ASSERT_DOUBLES_EQUAL(e.GetSigLogRatioHi(), e2.GetSigLogRatioHi(), 0.000001f);
00102         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(e.GetDetection() ==e2.GetDetection());
00103         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(e.GetNumPairs() ==e2.GetNumPairs());
00104         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(e.GetNumPairsUsed() ==e2.GetNumPairsUsed());
00105         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(e.GetHasComparisonData() ==e2.GetHasComparisonData());
00106         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(e.GetChange() ==e2.GetChange());
00107         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(e.GetCommonPairs() ==e2.GetCommonPairs());
00108 
00109 
00110         CHPBackgroundZone bgz;
00111         data2.GetBackgroundZone(0, bgz);
00112         CPPUNIT_ASSERT_DOUBLES_EQUAL(bgz.GetBackground(), bgz1.GetBackground(), 0.000001f);
00113         CPPUNIT_ASSERT_DOUBLES_EQUAL(bgz.GetCenterX(), bgz1.GetCenterX(), 0.000001f);

00243 void CHPFileWriterTest::WriteReseqTest()
00244 {
00245         CHPData data("CHP_reseq_file", CHP_RESEQUENCING_ASSAY_TYPE);
00246         data.SetEntryCount(5, 10);

00251         writer->SeekToDataSet();
00252         
00253         CHPReseqEntry e;
00254         e.call = 'a';
00255         e.score = 1.0f;
00256         writer->WriteReseqEntry(e);
00257         e.call = 'c';
00258         e.score = 2.0f;
00259         writer->WriteReseqEntry(e);
00260         e.call = 'g';
00261         e.score = 3.0f;
00262         writer->WriteReseqEntry(e);
00263         e.call = 't';
00264         e.score = 4.0f;
00265         writer->WriteReseqEntry(e);
00266         e.call = 'n';
00267         e.score = 5.0f;
00268         writer->WriteReseqEntry(e);
00269 
00270         writer->SeekToForceSet();
00271         CHPReseqForceCall force;
00272         force.position = 1;
00273         force.call = 'a';
00274         force.reason = CC_SATURATION_LEVEL_FORCE_CALL;
00275         writer->WriteForceCall(force);
00276         force.position = 2;
00277         force.call = 'c';
00278         force.reason = CC_WEAK_SIGNAL_THR_FORCE_CALL;
00279         writer->WriteForceCall(force);
00280 
00281         writer->SeekToOrigCallSet();
00282         CHPReseqOrigCall orig;
00283         orig.position = 3;
00284         orig.call = 't';
00285         writer->WriteOrigCall(orig);
00286         orig.position = 4;
00287         orig.call = 'a';
00288         writer->WriteOrigCall(orig);
00289         orig.position = 5;
00290         orig.call = 'g';
00291         writer->WriteOrigCall(orig);
00292 
00293         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(1);
00294 
00295         delete writer;
00296 
00297 
00298 
00299 
00300         CHPFileReader reader;
00301         reader.SetFilename("CHP_reseq_file");
00302         CHPData data2;
00303         reader.Read(data2);
00304 
00305         data2.GetEntry(0, e);
00306         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(e.call == 'a');
00307         CPPUNIT_ASSERT_DOUBLES_EQUAL(e.score, 1.0f, 0.0001f);
00308 
00309         data2.GetEntry(1, e);
00310         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(e.call == 'c');
00311         CPPUNIT_ASSERT_DOUBLES_EQUAL(e.score, 2.0f, 0.0001f);
00312 
00313         data2.GetEntry(2, e);
00314         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(e.call == 'g');
00315         CPPUNIT_ASSERT_DOUBLES_EQUAL(e.score, 3.0f, 0.0001f);
00316
